{
  "id": "672aa74f761c065c9828a95e",
  "title": "Šta je pseudo-klasa i kako funkcioniše?",
  "challengeType": 19,
  "dashedName": "what-are-pseudo-classes",
  "solutions": [],
  "nodules": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class je specifična ključna reč za CSS koja omogućava odabir elementa na osnovu njegovog specifičnog stanja ili položaja. Stanje ili položaj elementa može uključivati:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<ul>\n<li>Linapokuwa hai (active).</li>\n<li>Linapobofyozwa na panya.</li>\n<li>Linapokuwa mtoto wa kwanza wa mzazi.</li>\n<li>Linapokuwa mtoto wa mwisho wa mzazi.</li>\n<li>Linapokuwa kiungo kilichotembelewa.</li>\n<li>Linapokuwa limezimwa.</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Da biste koristili pseudo-class, dodajete ga u selektor koristeći dve tačke (<code>:</code>), praćene nazivom pseudo-class:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">selector:pseudo-class {\n  /* CSS properties */\n}\n</code></pre>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Istražite kako možete koristiti pseudo-class da predstavite svaku od stanja i lokacija koje smo pomenuli.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class od <code>:active</code> vam omogućava da izaberete stanje funkcionalne komponente, kao što je klik na dugme:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<button>Example Button</button>",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;button>Example Button&#x3C;/button>\n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": "button:active {\n  background: greenyellow;\n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">button:active {\n  background: greenyellow;\n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class za <code>:hover</code> opisuje stanje prelaska mišem elementa. Primer je kada kliknete na dugme ili link:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<a href=\"#\">Hover over me!</a>  ",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;a href=\"#\">Hover over me!&#x3C;/a>  \n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": "a:hover {\n  text-decoration: none;\n  color: white;\n  background: crimson;\n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">a:hover {\n  text-decoration: none;\n  color: white;\n  background: crimson;\n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class od <code>:first-child</code> bira element koji je prvi potomak svog roditelja. Evo primera ciljanja prvog pasusa unutar kontejnera <code>div</code>:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<div class=\"container\">\n  <p>first child</p>\n  <p>second child</p>\n  <p>third child</p>\n  <p>last child</p>\n</div>",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;div class=\"container\">\n  &#x3C;p>first child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>second child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>third child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>last child&#x3C;/p>\n&#x3C;/div>\n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": ".container p:first-child {\n  background: lightcoral;\n  padding: 0.4rem;\n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.container p:first-child {\n  background: lightcoral;\n  padding: 0.4rem;\n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Prvi pasus unutar elementa <code>div</code> dobiće pozadinsku boju <code>lightcoral</code> i <code>padding</code> od <code>0.4rem</code> sa svih strana.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class za <code>:last-child</code> cilja na poslednji element koji je dete svog roditelja. Evo primera ciljanja poslednjeg pasusa unutar kontejnera <code>div</code>:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<div class=\"container\">\n  <p>first child</p>\n  <p>second child</p>\n  <p>third child</p>\n  <p>last child</p>\n</div>",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;div class=\"container\">\n  &#x3C;p>first child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>second child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>third child&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;p>last child&#x3C;/p>\n&#x3C;/div>\n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": ".container p:last-child {\n  background: lightcoral;\n  padding: 0.4rem;\n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.container p:last-child {\n  background: lightcoral;\n  padding: 0.4rem;\n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class ya <code>:visited</code> omogućava vam da uredite link koji je korisnik već posetio:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<a href=\"https://www.example.com\" target=\"_blank\">Visit Example.com</a>",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;a href=\"https://www.example.com\" target=\"_blank\">Visit Example.com&#x3C;/a>\n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": "a:visited {\n  color: purple;\n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">a:visited {\n  color: purple;\n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Pseudo-class ya <code>:disabled</code> inakuwezesha kupangilia kipengele kinachoshirikiana kilichozimwa:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactiveEditor",
      "files": [
        {
          "contents": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n<button disabled>Disabled Button</button>",
          "ext": "html",
          "name": "index-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n&#x3C;button disabled>Disabled Button&#x3C;/button>\n</code></pre>"
        },
        {
          "contents": "button:disabled {\n  background-color: lightgray;  \n}",
          "ext": "css",
          "name": "styles-1",
          "contentsHtml": "<pre><code class=\"language-css\">button:disabled {\n  background-color: lightgray;  \n}\n</code></pre>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Kao što vidite, pseudo-class vam omogućavaju da organizujete elemente na osnovu interakcije korisnika, kao što je <em>hover</em> ili poseta linku. Ovo čini vaš sajt vizuelno interaktivnijim.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<p>Osim pseudo-class spomenutih, postoje i drugi slični:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "contents": "<ul>\n<li><code>:focus</code></li>\n<li><code>:first-of-type</code></li>\n<li><code>:last-of-type</code></li>\n<li><code>:nth-of-type</code></li>\n<li><code>:modal</code></li>\n<li><code>:enabled</code></li>\n<li><code>:checked</code></li>\n<li><code>:required</code>, više.</li>\n</ul>"
    }
  ],
